Helper Function for log_p11()

Source: R/corPFSOS.R
p11Integ.Rd

Helper Function for log_p11()

Usage

p11Integ(x, transition)

Arguments

x

(numeric)
variable of integration.

transition

(TransitionParameters)
see exponential_transition(), weibull_transition() or piecewise_exponential() for details.

Value

Hazard rate at the specified time for the transition from progression to death.
